author: The Current
description: Minneapolis music icon Mark Mallman‘s “Seen My Own Ghost” is a key track off his new paranormal concept album “Magic Time”. The writer, rocker, and historian celebrated his 11th studio album’s release on August 8. “Seen My Own Ghost” can be heard station-wide on The Current. Hit Play!
title: Mark Mallman talks about "Seen My Own Ghost" #MarkMallman #MagicTime

author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Fraea, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2016.
